heic-viewer — HEIC / HEIF support
=================================

This extension bundles `libheif-js` — an emscripten port of libheif — which
decodes HEIC/HEIF images (Apple's default photo format, HEVC/H.265-coded)
into RGBA pixels entirely in the browser via WebAssembly.

  libheif-js:   https://github.com/catdad-experiments/libheif-js
  libheif:      https://github.com/strukturag/libheif
  libde265:     https://github.com/strukturag/libde265  (the HEVC decoder)

